transcript:
Customer: Hello?

Executive: Hello?

Customer: Haan ji bhai.

Executive: Hello, haan sir, main Shubham bol raha hun, good morning, Jai Mata.

Customer: Haan, good morning, batao.

Executive: Main bol raha tha sir kya hua us topic mein resolve hui uski?

Customer: Nahi, kahan hua, abhi kuch aaya nahi hai.

Executive: To aapki team kya team ko aapne share kiya hai link wo?

Customer: Hmm.

Executive: Team ko link share kiya hai aapne?

Customer: Wo to jo aapne link bheja tha wahi bhej diya tha maine unhone.

Executive: Haan to bheja unko kuch isme nahi samajh mein aaya.

Customer: Main ek kaam karta hun din mein na main tumhari conference call mein ek baar baat kara deta hun.

Executive: Sir ye actually aap karwaiye aaj actually concern open hai na baar baar to iske ya to concern ek minute karenge aaj.

Executive: Theek hai, theek hai.

Executive: Usko bhejna nahi hai aati hai.
